description.originalText: Jaley has been extremely reliable. And my kids are always thrilled when she gets to come over. I would highly recommend Jaley!
Jaley is an excellent babysitter. My daughter always enjoys their time together and I find her reliable and very pleasant. I definitely recommend Jaley!

description.displayText: Jaley has been nannying for us for several months. She has changed our world for the better! My girls adore her! My three year old often asks if we can call Jaley because she misses her, and my 18 month old sometimes cries when she leaves. Jaley is super punctual, reliable, and has been so helpful in assisting us in a pinch and for various tasks (like driving kids around and arranging play dates). She has also been very capable in caring for all four of my children at once (ages 9, 6, 3, and 1). What really sets her apart from other caregivers is how capably she cleans and tidies main areas of our home while tending children. She knows how to engage my kids at their level, making their imaginary worlds come alive. I highly recommend Jaley and am grateful for the part she plays in our family!

description.displayText: Jaley nannied for us for about two years, and we absolutely loved her! She was super great at engaging with our children and making them feel loved. She stayed off her phone (We have issues with previous nannies on their phone the whole time). We always came home to a clean house. Which was huge for us, and made a big difference. She was always willing to run errands and do miscellaneous things for us. We are sad to see her move but so happy for her!!

description.displayText: Interviewed Jaley, was impressed during our phone conversation. However, when she came to meet our family in person, she was completely different than how she was over the phone. She did not have much energy and did not really fight for the job. When we discussed pay, we told her our rate was between $15-20 an hour (what we had on our profile) and she then told us she couldn't take anything less than $22 an hour, We offered her a certain amount and told her to think about and let us know over the next 2 days and of course she totally ghosted us. No replies and did not reject our offer
